{
  "design_notes": "Hard level chart meticulously crafted around the 115 BPM groove. The intro (bars 0-8) introduces players with sparse rhythmic steps that follow the main kicks. Verse 1 (bars 8-20) steps up to a continuous 8th-note stream with light crossover elements. Drop 1 (bars 20-32) pushes the jumpstream density to match the rising electronic energy. The climax (bars 32-40) incorporates fast eighth-note drill steps. In Verse 2 (bars 40-52), we transition into a moving runningman pattern. The final peak climax (bars 52-60) utilizes highly active jumpstreams before fading into a quiet breathing outro (bars 60-62) with minimalist steps to prevent dead space.",
